These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different games are played: go, bridge, chess
3 different pets are kept: rat, bird, ferret
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, october, april
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, fantasy, satire
City: rome, new-york, hannover
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, game, blend
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, amber, ivory
 1. the person who likes blood-red is the game-smoker##1
 2. the person who likes ivory is the person watching satire movies##1
 3. the person playing chess is between the blend-smoker and the person playing bridge##2
 4. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
 5. the person watching fantasy movies is the owner of the ferret##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is the fonseca-smoker##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 8. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 9. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Game      | bridge    | chess   | go           |
| Pet          | bird       | ferret    | rat         |
| Birthday         | october    | april  | january        |
| Movie-Genre           | drama | fantasy   | satire      |
| City   | new-york        | hannover    | rome       |
| Cigar   | game     | fonseca  | blend       |
| Color         | blood-red     | amber | ivory |

