The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, bike, taxi
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, begonia, amaryllis
3 different games are played: domino, canasta, billiard
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is the person driving the bike##1
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is the colonial house##1
 3. the colonial house is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 4. the person playing domino is between the firefighter and the security-guard##2
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
 6. the firefighter is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 8. the person traveling to venice is the victorian house##1
 9. the colonial house is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
10. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Job      | security-guard   | musician    | firefighter         |
| City          | venice    | london | boston          |
