The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, cycling
3 different games are played: billiard, snooker, monopoly
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, march, january
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 2. the person who growsaconite is the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 4. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 5. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person driving the trike and the person who growsaconite##2
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person traveling to rome##1
 8. the person eating lime is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person eating lime and the person eating spinach##2
10. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
| Flower      | aconite | balloon-flower           | bellflower      |
