There 3 different types of food: nectarine, peas, garlic
3 different games are played: go, snooker, scrabble
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, cain, swisher
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, white, yellow
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, soul, blues
 1. the person who likes yellow is in the middle##1
 2. the wooden house is in the middle##1
 3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 4. the person who growsrose is the person eating peas##1
 5. the fan punk is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 6. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 7. the fan blues is between the cape-cod house and the person playing go##2
 8. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 9. the person eating peas is the fan punk##1
10. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
11. the fan punk is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| House      | cape-cod | wooden      | victorian      |
| Flower         | tulip     | balloon-flower     | rose  |
| Food   | garlic | nectarine  | peas |
| Game   | snooker  | scrabble     | go |
| Cigar           | siglo        | swisher | cain     |
| Color         | lavender    | yellow | white   |
| Music-Genre     | soul        | blues        | punk   |

